features: ☉【3-Tier Over The Sink Dish Drying Rack】-Size: 33.5" W x 13.6" D x 32.2" H. Maximum Load: 45 Lbs. 3 Tier over sink dish drying rack makes good use of the space above the sink to keep your kitchen counter organized. The top of the dish drying rack can also be used as a storage rack for pans, spices, etc.

☉【Save Space & Keep Clean】-Our innovative Above Sink Dish Drying Rack with Cover not only provides extra protection for your drying dishes, but also keeps them clean. Large storage kitchen dish rack features 90° flip-up cabinet door for easy access to dishes.

☉【High Quality Material】-Our sink dish drying rack is constructed of high-quality metal, and the sturdy construction ensures stability and durability. The black surface coating ensures long-lasting performance. The thickened dish rack is stronger and more durable than ordinary dish racks on the market. The dish drainer has 4 suction cups under the feet to prevent dropping or shaking.

☉【Multifunctional Kitchen Organizer】-Multi-functional kitchen dish rack provides more space without spending more on countertop space. The dish rack above the sink holds a variety of dishes in a compact design with 7 removable parts. Including 1 dish rack, 1 bowl rack, 1 knife rack, 1 storage basket, 1 cutlery holder, 1 chopping board rack, and 8 hooks (4 for hanging on the sides and 4 for pegboard). Easy cleaning of all accessories.
☉【Easy to Assemble】-The Over Sink Dish Drying Rack is equipped with a hex key, no extra tools needed, easy to install. Follow the instructions, assemble the corresponding module.
